ate":"2021-10-20T05:19:50+0000","slugs":["challenger-un-ecosysteme-technique-medical-connecte","challenger-un-ecosysteme-technique-medicale-connecte","securite"],"linked_documents":[],"lang":"fr-fr","alternate_languages":[{"id":"YdL89RAAACMA4NTi","type":"reference","lang":"fr-ca"}],"data":{"title":"Challenger un écosystème technique médical connecté","date":"2021-10-19T22:00:00+0000","image":{"dimensions":{"width":338,"height":454},"alt":null,"copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/zenika-website/82ab357d-b9fa-4760-b2b4-a651c2a89ff7_ryan-plomp-0iPebSCgKoA-unsplash.jpg?auto=compress,format\u0026rect=483,0,954,1281\u0026w=338\u0026h=454"},"avatar":{},"quote":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"Le projet\nPour une solution médicale connectée de monitoring d'électrocardiogrammes, nous implémentons pour Bioserenity une démarche DevSecOps et une campagne de tests d'intrusion (web, mobile, hardware). Nous les avons ensuite accompagnés dans les corrections à mettre en oeuvre, suivi d'un contre audit validant la correction des vulnérabilités.","spans":[{"start":0,"end":10,"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Expertises\nAWS, MQTT, STM32, Spring, Angular","spans":[{"start":0,"end":10,"type":"strong"}]}],"author":null,"role":null,"url":{"link_type":"Any"}}},{"id":"YW7yShIAACwARXRU","uid":null,"url":null,"type":"reference","href":"https://zenika-website.cdn.prismic.io/api/v2/documents/search?ref=YoNRBRIAAC8AqzKB\u0026q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22YW7yShIAACwARXRU%22%29+%5D%5D","tags":[],"first_publication_date":"2021-10-20T05:18:44+0000","last_publication_date":"2021-10-20T09:45:14+0000","slugs":["deployer-une-culture-accelerate-en-quelques-mois"],"linked_documents":[],"lang":"fr-fr","alternate_languages":[{"id":"YdL89BAAACMA4NTc","type":"reference","lang":"fr-ca"}],"data":{"title":"Déployer une culture Accelerate en quelques mois","date":"2021-10-18T22:00:00+0000","image":{"dimensions":{"width":338,"height":454},"alt":null,"copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/zenika-website/7f07836f-5562-4fbf-83cc-ab5ec2179034_tomasz-frankowski-kBUfvkbFIoE-unsplash.jpg?auto=compress,format\u0026rect=484,0,953,1280\u0026w=338\u0026h=454"},"avatar":{},"quote":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"Le projet\nLes KPIs Accelerate doivent être des indices de l'accélération dans une organisation mais ne doivent pas être des objectifs. Pour reprendre la main sur le déploiement d'Accelerate chez un géant Français du E-commerce, nous avons crée un parcours pour apprendre aux équipes à utiliser cette approche. Ce parcours est en cours de déploiement à l'échelle.","spans":[{"start":0,"end":9,"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Expertises\nAccelerate, DevOps, Agilité, Coaching","spans":[{"start":0,"end":10,"type":"strong"}]}],"author":null,"role":null,"url":{"link_type":"Any"}}},{"id":"YWbRKhIAACkA37OJ","uid":null,"url":null,"type":"reference","href":"https://zenika-website.cdn.prismic.io/api/v2/documents/search?ref=YoNRBRIAAC8AqzKB\u0026q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22YWbRKhIAACkA37OJ%22%29+%5D%5D","tags":[],"first_publication_date":"2021-10-13T12:29:33+0000","last_publication_date":"2021-10-18T20:15:56+0000","slugs":["simplifier-les-processus-administratifs-pour-permettre-au-personnel-universitaire-de-se-concentrer-sur-lexperience-des-etudiants","comment-edf-a-t-il-gagne-le-pari-difficile-de-la-transformation-en-temps-et-en-heure-"],"linked_documents":[],"lang":"fr-fr","alternate_languages":[{"id":"YWcPlBIAAPJl4L0M","type":"reference","lang":"en-us"},{"id":"YdL8-RAAACMA4NT0","type":"reference","lang":"fr-ca"},{"id":"YdL9hRAAAJMQ4NY9","type":"reference","lang":"en-ca"},{"id":"YbsHuhUAADAAriUt","type":"reference","lang":"en-sg"}],"data":{"title":"Simplifier les processus administratifs pour permettre au personnel universitaire de se concentrer sur l'expérience des étudiants","date":"2021-10-17T22:00:00+0000","image":{"dimensions":{"width":338,"height":454},"alt":"Amphithéâtre universitaire ","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/zenika-website/03098c5d-0e17-4dc3-b72a-fec11e2284a7_dom-fou-YRMWVcdyhmI-unsplash.jpg?auto=compress,format\u0026rect=343,0,1072,1440\u0026w=338\u0026h=454"},"avatar":{},"quote":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"Le projet \nAprès un premier Audit de son SI, ICES a confié à Zenika le développement d'une solution spécifique adaptée, unifiée et flexible pour automatiser certaines tâches administratives, permettre de répondre à des pics de demandes tout au long de l'année universitaire, et faciliter la collaboration entre les services administratifs et les étudiants.","spans":[{"start":0,"end":10,"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Expertises\nGoogle Kubernetes Engine, Google Cloud, API Gateway, UX","spans":[{"start":0,"end":10,"type":"strong"}]}],"author":null,"role":null,"url":{"link_type":"Any"}}},{"id":"YWrb_RIAAAWk8X3N","uid":null,"url":null,"type":"reference","href":"https://zenika-website.cdn.prismic.io/api/v2/documents/search?ref=YoNRBRIAAC8AqzKB\u0026q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22YWrb_RIAAAWk8X3N%22%29+%5D%5D","tags":[],"first_publication_date":"2021-10-16T14:04:50+0000","last_publication_date":"2021-10-19T12:44:39+0000","slugs":["mutualiser-les-activites-de-rd-sur-la-thematique-du-greenit","mutualiser-des-activites-de-rd-sur-la-thematique-du-greenit"],"linked_documents":[],"lang":"fr-fr","alternate_languages":[{"id":"YW7tiBIAAC0ARWKF","type":"reference","lang":"en-us"},{"id":"YdL89xAAACEA4NTq","type":"reference","lang":"fr-ca"},{"id":"YbsHkRUAADIAriRx","type":"reference","lang":"en-sg"},{"id":"YdL9hBAAACEA4NY4","type":"reference","lang":"en-ca"}],"data":{"title":"Mutualiser les activités de R\u0026D sur la thématique du GreenIT","date":"2021-10-11T22:00:00+0000","image":{"dimensions":{"width":338,"height":454},"alt":"Green IT","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/zenika-website/ab661507-2b95-4872-9bc3-d0cc1dac97ae_nail-gilfanov-TuyneoFacJg-unsplash.jpg?auto=compress,format\u0026rect=604,0,953,1280\u0026w=338\u0026h=454"},"avatar":{},"quote":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"Le projet \nArkéa a consulté Zenika pour mettre en place une démarche de co-R\u0026D : sensibilisation au Green IT et à l'écoconception, production de prototypes fonctionnels, création d’application web d’inspiration LowTech, intégration d’outillages de mesure dans une plateforme d’intégration continue, constitution d’un référentiel de bonnes pratiques.","spans":[{"start":0,"end":10,"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Expertises \nGreen IT, formation, écoconception","spans":[{"start":0,"end":11,"type":"strong"}]}],"author":null,"role":null,"url":{"link_type":"Any"}}},{"id":"YWrcWBIAALSl8X9k","uid":null,"url":null,"type":"reference","href":"https://zenika-website.cdn.prismic.io/api/v2/documents/search?ref=YoNRBRIAAC8AqzKB\u0026q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22YWrcWBIAALSl8X9k%22%29+%5D%5D","tags":[],"first_publication_date":"2021-10-16T14:06:19+0000","last_publication_date":"2021-10-19T12:45:43+0000","slugs":["faciliter-la-souscription-de-contrats-dassurance-contre-les-aleas-climatiques","faciliter-la-souscription-de-contrats-dassurance-contre-les-aleas-climatiques."],"linked_documents":[],"lang":"fr-fr","alternate_languages":[{"id":"YW7R8RIAAHDvAsSk","type":"reference","lang":"en-us"},{"id":"YdL89hAAAJMQ4NTn","type":"reference","lang":"fr-ca"},{"id":"YbsHXhUAAC0AriN2","type":"reference","lang":"en-sg"},{"id":"YdL9ghAAAIAW4NYz","type":"reference","lang":"en-ca"}],"data":{"title":"Faciliter la souscription de contrats d'assurance contre les aléas climatiques","date":null,"image":{"dimensions":{"width":338,"height":454},"alt":"Aléas climatiques","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/zenika-website/09ec9aee-8858-430a-aace-7cc4a6d8edbd_luka-vovk-EngLPePzg7U-unsplash.jpg?auto=compress,format\u0026rect=0,17,1920,2579\u0026w=338\u0026h=454"},"avatar":{},"quote":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"Le projet \nUne équipe de consultants a accompagné une célèbre compagnie d'assurances pour réaliser 